reviewText: The DVD is pretty good although I prefer some of my older dvd's.  Part of it may be that I am more comfortable with them from practice.

this a kick butt workout.  even after one 6 min segment i was tired.  i got this set along with the book and they really go well together.  the book has a week schedule of what workouts to do for your body type.  the nice thing is you fit them in when you can.  this is a must for moms who want to get back in shape and feel short on time.  i love that the moms in the workout are real, not perfect models.  it is realistic and fun!
